{
  "_설명": "Windows 7+ 실외 날씨 중계 exe (pkg node12-win-x64). MES mes-prod-viewer.exe 와 별도.",
  "buildCommand": "npm run build:relay-exe",
  "prerequisites": {
    "os": "Windows x64 (빌드하는 PC, Node 18+ 권장)",
    "runtimeTarget": "Windows 7 SP1 이상 (119 PC 등, Node 설치 불필요)"
  },
  "entryPoint": "./relay/outdoor-relay.js",
  "includedScripts": ["./relay/outdoor-relay.js", "./relay/openMeteo.js", "./relay/httpUtil.js"],
  "pkgTarget": "node12-win-x64",
  "output": {
    "directory": "./dist",
    "exePath": "./dist/outdoor-relay.exe"
  },
  "deployment": [
    "npm run build:relay-exe → dist/outdoor-relay.exe + outdoor-relay.env.example + VBS/PS1",
    "119 PC: outdoor-relay.exe, outdoor-relay.env (Win7), start-outdoor-relay-hidden.vbs",
    "MES ENV_OUTDOOR_INGEST_KEY = OUTDOOR_INGEST_KEY",
    "작업 스케줄러: VBS 경로 등록 (콘솔 창 없이 상시 실행)",
    "Push만: RELAY_HTTP=0 / Pull: RELAY_HTTP=1 + 방화벽 8080",
    "Open-Meteo: tempC(기온), feelsLikeC(체감), humidityPct, 3일 예보"
  ]
}
